{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784851294919,"sessionID":"ses_06e92b9e1ffe3dG0tYh0vdFLNP","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"chatcmpl-tool-a9db5c66727cbcc3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/workspace/README.md","limit":200},"output":"<path>/workspace/README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # RemixHub\n2: \n3: **RemixHub** is a platform for discovering and creating authentic brand stories through AI‑driven content remixing.\n4: \n5: ## Overview\n6: - **Backend**: FastAPI (Python 3.11) running in Docker.\n7: - **AI/NLP**: TensorFlow & HuggingFace Transformers (distil‑BERT) for trend classification and content generation.\n8: - **Data pipeline**: Kafka → Spark Structured Streaming → PostgreSQL for time‑series storage.\n9: - **Auth & Ops**: OAuth2 for social logins, AWS Lambda for webhook handling, CloudWatch for monitoring.\n10: \n11: ## Core APIs\n12: - `POST /trends` – retrieve behavior‑verified trends.\n13: - `POST /generate` – generate brand‑compliant copy, hashtags and visual prompts.\n14: - `POST /dispatch` – queue content for social platforms (Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn).\n15: \n16: ## Quick Start\n17: ```bash\n18: # Build and start services\n19: docker compose up --build -d\n20: \n21: # Test API (example)\n22: curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/trends -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"query\": \"sustainability\"}'\n23: ```\n24: \n25: Further implementation details (trend engine, NLP core, dispatcher) are TODOs in the code.\n\n(End of file - total 25 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# RemixHub\n\n**RemixHub** is a platform for discovering and creating authentic brand stories through AI‑driven content remixing.\n\n## Overview\n- **Backend**: FastAPI (Python 3.11) running in Docker.\n- **AI/NLP**: TensorFlow & HuggingFace Transformers (distil‑BERT) for trend classification and content generation.\n- **Data pipeline**: Kafka → Spark Structured Streaming → PostgreSQL for time‑series storage.\n- **Auth & Ops**: OAuth2 for social logins, AWS Lambda for webhook handling, CloudWatch for monitoring.\n\n## Core APIs\n- `POST /trends` – retrieve behavior‑verified trends.\n- `POST /generate` – generate brand‑compliant copy, hashtags and visual prompts.\n- `POST /dispatch` – queue content for social platforms (Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn).\n\n## Quick Start\n```bash\n# Build and start services\ndocker compose up --build -d\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/workspace/README.md","text":"# RemixHub\n\n**RemixHub** is a platform for discovering and creating authentic brand stories through AI‑driven content remixing.\n\n## Overview\n- **Backend**: FastAPI (Python 3.11) running in Docker.\n- **AI/NLP**: TensorFlow & HuggingFace Transformers (distil‑BERT) for trend classification and content generation.\n- **Data pipeline**: Kafka → Spark Structured Streaming → PostgreSQL for time‑series storage.\n- **Auth & Ops**: OAuth2 for social logins, AWS Lambda for webhook handling, CloudWatch for monitoring.\n\n## Core APIs\n- `POST /trends` – retrieve behavior‑verified trends.\n- `POST /generate` – generate brand‑compliant copy, hashtags and visual prompts.\n- `POST /dispatch` – queue content for social platforms (Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn).\n\n## Quick Start\n```bash\n# Build and start services\ndocker compose up --build -d\n\n# Test API (example)\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:8000/trends -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"query\": \"sustainability\"}'\n```\n\nFurther implementation details (trend engine, NLP core, dispatcher) are TODOs in the code.","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":25,"totalLines":25,"truncated":false}},"title":"README.md","time":{"start":1784851294900,"end":1784851294916}},"id":"prt_f916d6a25001BEYcdOrAtJfRUe","sessionID":"ses_06e92b9e1ffe3dG0tYh0vdFLNP","messageID":"msg_f916d6623001ypVnAPVPR32v4I"}}
