{"type":"text","timestamp":1784851371973,"sessionID":"ses_06e92b9e1ffe3dG0tYh0vdFLNP","part":{"id":"prt_f916e911f0011aCmxONb69Sq1Y","messageID":"msg_f916e8e04001v54PgY9EY0DhOi","sessionID":"ses_06e92b9e1ffe3dG0tYh0vdFLNP","type":"text","text":"Implemented core enhancements:\n\n- **Policy Check**: Added `policy_check.py` with a simple banned‑word filter and `is_content_safe` function.\n- **Content Generation**: Integrated safety check into `ContentGen.generate`, returning a `safe` flag.\n- **Dispatcher Logging**: Updated `SocialDispatcher` to record dispatch attempts with timestamps and expose `get_logs`.\n- **API Extensions**: Added `/dispatch/logs` endpoint to retrieve in‑memory logs.\n- **README**: Expanded Quick‑Start examples to cover trends, generation, dispatch, and log retrieval.\n- **Code Cleanup**: Consolidated imports, removed duplicate docstrings, and improved documentation/comments.\n\nAll changes are committed. The API now provides basic safety validation, logging, and additional visibility for debugging and monitoring.","time":{"start":1784851370271,"end":1784851371968}}}
